Robin...
I never use protection...and have had a problem with a spirit that came
home with us from Waverly.  He&#39;s gone now, with the help of a great
individual.  I have evp&#39;s of this entity saying horrible things.  I think
I may start using protection now...

Carol B.








&gt; As someone who has never used a protection ritual (even though I consider
&gt; myself a very spiritual person), I&#39;m not sure I understand what the ritual
&gt; is intended to protect the person invoking it from.  I&#39;m not being a smart
&gt; ass; I&#39;m simply trying to learn.  Can we be hurt physically or psychically
&gt; by certain spirits, or can our experimentation open a dark portal that&#39;s
&gt; not meant to be opened?  My instinct has always been that if I don&#39;t
&gt; acknowledge evil it can have no power over me, but perhaps that&#39;s
&gt; ignorant.  I once invited spirits into my house from outside and
&gt; immediately recorded a negative EVP while heating a cup of coffee in the
&gt; microwave.  I was too ecstatic to be frightened by the message, but since
&gt; then I&#39;ve wondered what kind of spirit would want to say such a thing to
&gt; me and if I should be more cautious in the future.  I would love some
&gt; feedback on this recording.
&gt;
&gt; Robin
